name: Things We Lost to The Water [01]
description:
Water in the pond drying
For it turned into vapors.
In a few days
No water will be there.
Yet the clouds seen
At the distance turned away
To other directions
In the shallow water
Of the pond
Fishes are seen
Swimming here and there.
But oh Clouds,
Where you have flown!

- Akham Nilabirdhwaja Singh
